  "title": "Crafted Madness: Modern Era",
  "description": "Crafted Madness is and Expert Modpack designed to have an exagerated progression line and difficulty. It's based around GregTech",
  "body": "![Crafted Madness: Modern Era](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/CQzXK5KT/images/2f95dca3f5be5163731d92af0beefef59acd2a8e.png)\n# About\nCrafted Madness: Modern Era is and Expert Kitchen-sink Modpack designed to be very challenging and it's targeting players who enjoy grinding\n\nThis modpack is currently work in progress. Many changes will be made in the future. Also the modpack is unbalanced for now and many recipes needs change.\n\n# The main features in this modpack:\nThe hard recipes and progression line. Most of recipes got buffed (even gregtech ones) and some have multiple steps to be able to obtain it. Also some of the blocks & tools got nerfed to make the progress even harder.\n\nThe difficulty of the modpack in general. The mobs are buffed and the hard recipes makes the night very hard to survive and the caves very challenging to explore.\n\nThe unusual feeling of the modpack. This modpack description might seems like a GT:NH port for modern version but this modpack wasn't made to be \"GT:NT Modern\". Unlike GT:NH, Crafted Madness has a different progression and playing style\n\n# Mods\nThis modpack has over 400 mods (latest version). <br>\n<details>\n  <summary> Mods 4.0 </summary>\n<ul>\n\t<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/uJ9afomy\">AE2 Crystal Science</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/qelfSMnn\">AE2 Insert Export Card</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/projects/1150075\">AE2 MEGA Things</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/qVB0pZyA\">AE2 Pattern Encoding Access Terminal</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/gpwwX5bd\">AE2 Tangible Bookmarks</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/projects/609977\">AE2 Things</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/7GNdjsfs\">AE2 Toggleable View Cell</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/projects/961856\">AE2NetworkAnalyzer</a></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/pNabrMMw\">AE2WTLib</a></li>\n\t<li